spans.text: While at thy voice clear-cheeked Hygeia rears Her aqueous altars on this tepid coast
a cheerful Dome , Whose Lares smile
the light surface of the sandy mound
the firm texture of her amber Isle
thundering SHIPWRECK yell her dire decrees
Like leafless forests , on its verge extreme
the air , Tinge the soft seas of glass
the air , Tinge the soft seas of glass
he led To deathless glory their embattled Powers
To deathless glory their embattled Powers
That long on him clear-cheeked Hygeia's smile , And long on all he loves
